          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"totzeit-approximation-mit-pade\">Totzeit-Approximation mit Pad\u00e9</h1>\n<h2 id=\"totzeit-dead-time\">Totzeit (Dead Time)</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Eine ideale Totzeit verz\u00f6gert das Signal um <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(T_t||)</marimo-tex> Sekunden:</span>\n<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||[G(s) = e^{-T_t \\cdot s}||]</marimo-tex><span class=\"paragraph\">Problem: Nicht-rationale Funktion \u2192 schwer zu simulieren!</span>\n<h2 id=\"pade-approximation\">Pad\u00e9-Approximation</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Approximiert die Totzeit als rationale Funktion:</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>1. Ordnung:</strong>\n<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(G(s) \\approx \\frac{1 - \\frac{T_t}{2} s}{1 + \\frac{T_t}{2} s}||)</marimo-tex>||)</marimo-tex></span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>2. Ordnung:</strong>\n<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(<marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(G(s) \\approx \\frac{1 - \\frac{T_t}{2} s + \\frac{T_t^2}{12} s^2}{1 + \\frac{T_t}{2} s + \\frac{T_t^2}{12} s^2}||)</marimo-tex>||)</marimo-tex></span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
